{"tid":1655421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"古迦進行曲","createTime":"2019-10-15T05:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T06:26:01.000Z","uid":154443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef9481f37384983ca15540546b05dc9f29618e9","tid":1655421,"uid":154443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"蒙面法例過左，<br />\n林鄭要令香港進入白色恐怖<br />\n無視市民上街，防暴見人放彈<br />\n濫暴 班狗亂咁捉 隨時冇命<br />\n<br />\n黑衫夠勇武開遮反送中<br />\n黑衫起飛腿救人質<br />\n黑衫要打到班狗冇藥醫<br />\n<br />\nNo fear no pain<br />\n冇懼犧牲，狗仔只識發癲<br />\n<br />\nNo fear no pain<br />\n和勇不分，一於戰鬥到底<br />\n<br />\n全民凝聚，被捕手足要每日傳頌<br />\n香港人，個個遍地開花"},{"pid":"962f61f335b7b61034b1d64cd2187f82ba681d73","tid":1655421,"uid":154443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:05:23.000Z","msg":"自推（1/5）"},{"pid":"01b779a31ee13f7a7154099816c3693f8bcb7de7","tid":1655421,"uid":154443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"自推（2/5）"},{"pid":"fd658104f0f753d94edbac484a427dd0abcba462","tid":1655421,"uid":154443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:06:09.000Z","msg":"自推（3/5）"},{"pid":"22aaad80f44dcb9ddd1671f3ea08dd3f20b68a14","tid":1655421,"uid":327999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:06:40.000Z","msg":"高汁 推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c908f7145ce51bbe64fc750c4dff70be003a5581","tid":1655421,"uid":154443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"自推（4/5）"},{"pid":"3eb3e474d8ee75e6dbe56bc403536c44f536f986","tid":1655421,"uid":154443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:07:14.000Z","msg":"自推（5/5）"},{"pid":"7c6e6ac36c2bbaa6e5a88239134958d67f0432d9","tid":1655421,"uid":154443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:16:23.000Z","msg":"再推（1/5）"},{"pid":"